<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">٢ في الأًصل:</span> <span class="c1">"أولم"</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>